title: OCT2015_Calibration
description: Model details (10OCT2023) Version 6.3.1 - Model developer: HDR Engineering, Inc.  (Modeling lead: Ric McCallan) - Units: Horizontal and vertical units in US Feet - Horizontal Datum: North American Datum 1983, 2011 adjustment (NAD83 (2011))   - Calibration run for October 2015 event.  - Geometry calibration regions to final calibrated values for channels and overbanks - Precipitation, wind, and infiltration included.  - Variable stage boundary conditions included for downstream Gulf boundary. - Flow hydrograph included for the Main Atchafalaya Channel at Simmesport, LA. - Initial timestep based on final timestep of restart simulation.  - 2012 Existing Conditions Geometry - base grid cells 1000x1000, refinement included for streams and other key terrain features.  - Time step controlled by courant condition
